\v 14  \w Now|strong="H6258"\w* \w you|strong="H6258"\w* say, ‘\w Go|strong="H3212"\w* \w and|strong="H3212"\w* say \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w your|strong="H2026"\w* master, “Elijah \w is|strong="H2009"\w* \w back|strong="H3212"\w*,”’ \w but|strong="H2009"\w* \w he|strong="H3212"\w* will \w kill|strong="H2026"\w* \w me|strong="H2026"\w*.”  
