\v 20  Each \w one|strong="H4422"\w* \w struck|strong="H5221"\w* \w down|strong="H5221"\w* \w an|strong="H5221"\w* enemy soldier; \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Syrians \w fled|strong="H5127"\w* \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* \w chased|strong="H7291"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w*. \w King|strong="H4428"\w* Ben Hadad \w of|strong="H4428"\w* Syria \w escaped|strong="H4422"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w horseback|strong="H5483"\w* \w with|strong="H5921"\w* some \w horsemen|strong="H6571"\w*.  
