\v 17  Micaiah said, “\w I|strong="H7200"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* \w scattered|strong="H6327"\w* \w on|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w mountains|strong="H2022"\w* \w like|strong="H1004"\w* \w sheep|strong="H6629"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* \w shepherd|strong="H7462"\w*. \w Then|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* said, ‘\w They|strong="H1992"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* master. \w They|strong="H1992"\w* \w should|strong="H3068"\w* \w go|strong="H7725"\w* \w home|strong="H1004"\w* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w peace|strong="H7965"\w*.’”  
